        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/wet/scene_rat_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 9cb72ee8-0c21-4206-95db-7524a2170b41).Image",
        "Description": "In the hallowed halls of strategy, the “Omniscient Oracle’s Edict” reigns supreme. This contract, a testament to unparalleled acumen, decrees the silent descent of two guardians. Their fall, orchestrated by the unseen hand of fate, shall unfold with the precision of a grandmaster’s final move in a game of cosmic chess.   The alchemical use of soporifics and emetic concoctions is eschewed, and the vulgar resort to ballistic wounding is equally prosribed.\r\rSusnain decrees it to be so.",
